<a name="toc_tc29537"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P236-34: TestCaseWBT_Invalid_ValidareReteta&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">maria_salejan05</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se creeaza o noua reteta.</p>

<p>id&lt;=0</p>

<p>Lista de ingrediente este goala.</p>

<p>Se valideaza reteta.</p>

<p>In urma validarii se va arunca o exceptie cu mesajul &quot;Product ID invalid!\n Lista de ingrediente este goala\n&quot;</p>
